SOFTWARE SPOTLIGHT - Index Generator

Index Generator is a freeware tool that automatically gener-
ates asite map for your site. It's very fast too, just point 
it to the directory(folder) on your computer that you want it 
to generate an index fromand in a few seconds it will be a 
done deal for you.

It can create a structured site map, A-Z index, foldertree 
site maps,bibliographies and more. It pulls the title from 
your page as the linktext, and a page description from your 
meta description tag, saving a great deal of time and effort. 
Great little tool.

http://www.tildemh.com/sw/idgen/index.shtml

Note: I do not provide support for the software listed in 
this column.Contact the software vendor for support. Soft-
ware featured here issoftware that I or my stooges have 
tried and found to it be useful.

